And thats exactly what they did, the claws digging into the energy 
beings face and skull creating deep gash marks while making a 
greenish liquid pour from the wounds. Energy beings were very 
resistant to energy attacks however, physical ones were the weakness 
of them. Hellpeon shriked in pain before he latched his hands onto 
Ultimos claws trying to push him away.
